h3. Expected Behavior
Installs Agile

h3. Actual Behavior
The screen darkens and loads indefinitely, on the browser's console we can see a JavaScript error message (see screenshot).

!bug_agile_jira648.png|thumbnail!

h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Install JIRA;
# Click the link "Install JIRA Agile for project management" on the "Guide for JIRA Administrators" gadget at JIRA's System Dashboard while logged in as a System Administrator;

h3. Workaround
The current workaround is to install Agile through the other available ways, either through UPM (1) or by clicking "Agile" on the top bar (2).
h4. Workaround #1
# Go to *Administration* > *Add-ons* > *Find new add-ons*;
# Search for *JIRA Agile*;
# Install;

h4. Workaround #2
# Click the *Agile* item on JIRA's top bar;
# Click *Install JIRA Agile* on the pop-up;

